data.description: Updated Craftsman in the Heart of North Tacoma Buckley District. Enter into an open layout with 9ft ceilings & excellent natural light through the oversized windows. Kitchen features extensive custom wood cabinets, beautiful granite counters & stainless steel appliances. Primary bedroom on the main floor, with ensuite bathroom & large walk-in closet. Additional full bathroom on the main. Three full bedrooms on the upper floor, with a remodeled bathroom & extra loft/bonus room. Newer roof & upgraded vinyl windows throughout. Basement storage/workshop. Alley access with extensive private parking; perfect space for a wide garage &/or DADU. Amazing location, walking distance to 6th Ave, Stadium, schools & so much more! 3.5% assumable FHA loan!
